## ğŸ“‚ Project Structure

cmd/game/ # Entry point demo binary 
internal/engine # Core engine packages 
internal/esc # Camera component/system 
             # Physics system and colliders 
             # Mesh generation and handling 
             # Material component and shader integration 
assets/shaders/ # GLSL shader files
go.mod, go.sum # Go module definitions

